sections.text:
77-3134.Nebraska Shortline Rail Modernization Act, how cited.

Sections 77-3134 to 77-3143 shall be known and may be cited as the Nebraska Shortline Rail Modernization Act.

SourceLaws 2024, LB937, ยง 14.
